item.title: CVE-2019-0281|2024-08-04T17:44:16.570Z -- sap%20se -- openui5
item.description: SAPUI5 and OpenUI5, before versions 1.38.39, 1.44.39, 1.52.25, 1.60.6 and 1.63.0, does not sufficiently encode user-controlled inputs, resulting in Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.
